#I am just going to write some high-level topics that we should concentrate for the paper.
1. Introduction
2. Background
3. Proposed Idead
4. Experiment Details (experiment procedure, data collection)
5. Results & Discucssions
6. Conclusions & Future Work
7. References

The page limit is 4-6 pages in IEEE paper format

